      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars"><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i></div>
        <p class="review-text">"The customer service is outstanding. They helped me with a return within hours. Highly recommended platform!"</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">SP</div><div><strong>Sarah P.</strong><span>Verified Buyer</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars"><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i><i class="fas fa-star filled"></i></div>
        <p class="review-text">"Best prices on electronics I've found anywhere. The checkout process was smooth and secure. Will definitely shop again!"</p>
        <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">MK</div><div><strong>Michael K.</strong><span>Verified Buyer</span></div></div>
      </div>
